Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:17.25,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Like a fish skimming along a moonlit ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:22.12,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ran the train gently swaying from side to side.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:25.50,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Looking out, the scenery is quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:28.04,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,slipping by and then there's me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:31.29,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,just out there, a pair of eyes, a pair of eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:33.29,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,The waning evening, dyed in orange light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:37.41,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,and ruled over by the setting sun. I saw it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:40.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,swallowed up and buried in the overwhelming indigo sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:44.45,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,I had to run after the last ray of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.45,0:00:47.83,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,shining light chasing a memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:50.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,because now it's goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:59.50,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving on a journey to abandon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:01.33,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,tomorrow far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:02.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Bought a one-way ticket and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:06.04,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,decided to go far as I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:08.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,There's no place where I belong right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:12.37,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,so I'll just lose myself in the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:15.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,in the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.41,0:01:19.04,Lyrics-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,700)}Adrift
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:25.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, all the window shown before me was dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:28.60,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,And then I knew what I saw must be the view of the night sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:31.12,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\4a&H90}On a whim I stopped by a beach town,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:33.50,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,driven on. By unknown forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.50,0:01:36.12,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Waves guiding my way, or maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.12,0:01:38.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,someone was calling my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:39.54,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,to the seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:40.47,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:43.16,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,I think this could very well end up being my home and resting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Imagining all what I would do,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.79,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,you suddenly called to me out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:50.41,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Under the bright moonlight, pale-skinned and ghostly fair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:52.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,in a white one-piece dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:55.47,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,"What are you doing here at this time of night?",
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.72,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,you asked me with an inspecting glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:59.64,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,I'll try and keep it short for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:00.50,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,"I'm here for the sea."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:07.22,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,After that you took out from behind your back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:12.16,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a long unused set of fireworks for play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:15.83,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,That's when I saw and noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:17.83,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,you were walking barefoot on the concrete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:20.33,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,You didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:27.06,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,I had decided this day would be the one I'd end it all for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:31.16,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,So maybe I'm already gone and have stumbled into the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.93,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Maybe this meeting's just an apparition
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:37.41,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but this night, together we went and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:41.08,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,lit those antique fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.45,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,As hard as I tried my firework wouldn't light,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:51.50,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,so you got closer to share the flame
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:56.33,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,and rightly guessed my reason and motive for being here so far from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:58.41,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,You kept on encouraging me and urging not to go through with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:02.50,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,"please don't do it."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:04.98,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\4a&H90}"But I..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:09.79,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\4a&H90}And that's when a dazzling burst of light came from my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\4a&H90}The firework was ignited and we both jumped up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:14.58,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\4a&H90}and screamed "it's lit!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:17.41,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,The loud, crackling firework broke through the night air shining and dazzling
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:21.41,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,sinking deep in my senses
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,in my senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:26.33,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shining bright and intense before us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.25,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but then dimming and fading as quickly as it came.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:32.33,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Before I could burn the sight into my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.25,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,again I'd be left in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:35.87,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,I'd chase it desperately
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:40.54,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,like the twilight evening on my train to nowhere
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:43.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,into nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:47.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,I just can't. I'd end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:53.25,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me the answer to this one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:03.16,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Are you going to disappear when the morning comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:12.37,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Finally I walked right past the curtain of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:16.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Waking up, rubbing my eyes with the morning light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:22.64,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,To the side I looked and there, as if nothing important just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.25,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,You were lying there.
